reviewText: Good tips from some of the top bodybuilders.
I got this for our gym and it's really a bargain. Great info and workouts for folks to learn from.
This is a good DVD but a Better Training DVD would be "Critical Mass POF" Best training DVD ever made. With the POF DVD you will learn what the Bodybuilding Pros already know.

DVD arrived in time and without any damage.
Not at single scratch or problem on the DVD.
The DVD has been a good training aide.
